>
> ***Divine Awareness.*** Velik knows if he hears a lie.
>
> ***Honed Angelic Weapons.*** Velik's weapon attacks are magical. When Velik uses any weapon, the weapon deals an extra 8d8 radiant damage (included in the attack).
