> ## Caelum "The Sun Emperor"
>*Large celestial, lawful good*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 22 (natural armor)
> - **Hit Points** 752 (52d10 + 468)
> - **Speed** 50 ft., fly 150 ft.
>___
